Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel-cell oxygen gauge (Westinghouse model 203C) has been modified to improve output stability and to provide more efficient sample gas transport with shorter response times.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES

Sentencas: Conversion of the logarithmic output of the cell to a more convenient linear output has been achieved.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES

Sentencas: Evaluation of the modified instrument by comparison with Scholander analyses indicates a mean difference between the two methods of .008 vol% with a standard deviation of .015 vol%.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES

Sentencas: The instrument is linear over a range of oxygen concentrations from 1.0 to 99.6% O2.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES

Sentencas: The fuel cell provides continuous or single-breath analysis with a 0-90% response time of 0.20 sec.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES

Sentencas: The instrument which is small in size, simple to use, and capable of continuous and accurate analysis should prove of considerable value in physiological investigations.
Titulo: A MODIFIED FUEL CELL FOR ANALYSIS OF OXYGEN CONCENTRATION OF GASES
